@REM KEY 0 0 "Main" "The internal processing"
@{U}8) The internal processing@{UU}

   This chapter  describes  the  internal  processing of  Laplace.  I  try  to
explain, how Laplace works  and which algorithms are  used. Usually you  don't
need these informations, but if you  want to do some more complex  operations,
this could be interesting.

   @{" * " LINK "InternalIntro"}  Preface
   @{" * " LINK "InternalNumInt"}  Numerical integration


